//code.visualstudio.com/), Cursor ships with a familiar interface that developers already know while layering powerful AI capabilities on top. With over **1 million users** and 360,000 paying customers – including teams at half of the Fortune 500 – Cursor AI has proven itself well beyond the early-adopter phase. This **cursor tutorial** walks you through every essential feature in 12 structured steps, giving you a complete foundation for productive, AI-assisted development.\n\n### Table of Contents\n\n1.   [Prerequisites and System Requirements](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-0)\n2.   [Step 1: Download and Install Cursor](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-1)\n\n    1.   [Installing on macOS](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-2)\n    2.   [Installing on Windows](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-3)\n    3.   [Installing on Linux](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-4)\n\n3.   [Step 2: Import VS Code Settings and Extensions](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-5)\n4.   [Step 3: Configure Your AI Model](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-6)\n5.   [Step 4: Master Tab Completion](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-7)\n6.   [Step 5: Use Inline Editing with Cmd+K](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-8)\n7.   [Step 6: Use Chat for Codebase Queries](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-9)\n\n    1.   [The @Mention Context System](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-10)\n    2.   [Chat History and Context Window Management](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-11)\n\n8.   [Step 7: Build Multi-File Features with Composer](https://tech-insider.org/cursor-tutorial-ai-code-editor-2026#toc-12)\n9.   [Step 8: Set Up .cursorrules 